.Dd $Mdocdate: January 13 2017 $
.Dt VMMCI 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm vmmci
.Nd VMM control interface
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "vmmci* at virtio?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides a control interface for virtual machines running inside
.Ox
.Xr vmm 4
(virtual machine monitor)
hosts.
.Pp
The driver handles shutdown and reboot requests from the
.Xr vmm 4
host by signalling
.Xr init 8
with
.Dv SIGUSR2
and
.Dv SIGINT
respectively.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr pvbus 4 ,
.Xr vmm 4 ,
.Xr init 8 ,
.Xr vmd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.1 .
.Sh AUTHORS
The
.Nm
driver was written by
